problem_data.title: K-th Smallest in Lexicographical Order
problem_data.description: Given two integers n and k, return the kth lexicographically smallest integer in the range [1, n].

examples.explanation: The lexicographical order is [1, 10, 11, 12, 13, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8, 9], so the second smallest number is 10.
